PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of ROGER SOLOMAN, of Souris, Prince Edward Island, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Museum of Science and Technology to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Kenneth C. Lee, whose term has expired.
